      <title>法赫米：停火让哈马斯有机会与特朗普政府合作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/fahmy-ceasefire-gives-hamas-an-in-with-trump-admin-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据报道，以色列和哈马斯“原则上”同意了一项停火协议，该协议可能最早在本周完成。长岛大学国际关系与外交主任兼政治学副教授达莉亚·法赫米 (Dalia Fahmy) 向彭博社《地平线》中东和非洲主播乔曼娜·贝尔塞切 (Joumanna Bercetche) 解释了为什么这项协议这次可能会获得批准。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/fahmy-ceasefire-gives-hamas-an-in-with-trump-admin-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:46:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴罗佐：欧盟应继续与中国进行贸易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/barroso-eu-should-continue-to-trade-with-china-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[前欧盟委员会主席、高盛国际顾问公司主席若泽·曼努埃尔·巴罗佐认为，如果欧盟停止与中国的贸易，将对欧洲、中国乃至世界经济造成损害。他在高盛 2025 年亚太全球宏观会议间隙与 Minmin Low 和 Haslinda Amin 进行了交谈。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-15/barroso-eu-should-continue-to-trade-with-china-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 05:01:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场等待美国 CPI 测试，比特币受到科技股的启发</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</link>
      <description><![CDATA[比特币与美国科技股指数之间的相关性已达到两年来的最高水平，这表明股市对周三晚些时候公布的美国通胀数据的反应可能为数字代币定下基调。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-15/bitcoin-btc-nasdaq-100-correlation-at-two-year-high-before-us-cpi</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 15 Jan 2025 01:36:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
